text: Pașcani is a city in Iași County, Romania. It is on the river Siret. As of 2021, 30,766 people live in Pașcani. The name comes from the estate of the boyar Oană Pașca. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Cities in Romania Category:Municipalities of Romania Category:Iași County
